<section id="free-event">
  <img src="/images/free-event-1.png" alt="free-event" width="25" height="49" />
  <a href="#registration"><img src="/images/free-event-2.png" alt="free-event" width="82" height="49" /></a>
  <img src="/images/free-event-3.png" alt="free-event" width="353" height="49" />
</section>

<section id="main">
  <div id="descriptions" class="clearfix">
    <section id="what">
      <header>
        <h2>What</h2>
      </header>
      <p>
        <%= Registration.count %> high school and college students will gather on a winter Saturday to talk about making
        web and mobile applications. In-demand technologies will be introduced by accomplished folks.
        Designers and developers from hiring web startups will be available to meet students after
        the talks. <%= link_to "Learn more.", page_path("what") %>
      </p>
    </section>
    <div id="divider">
      <img src="/images/description-divider.png" alt="description-divider" width="48" height="174" />
    </div>
    <section id="why">
      <header>
        <h2>Why</h2>
      </header>
      <p>
        There is a shortage of great designers and developers in Boston, San Francisco, and New York
        right now as startup demand has increased dramatically. They need the next generation to
        join them in creating the latest technological revolutions in information and telecommunications.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
  <hr class="bottom"/>
  <section id="event-location">
    <div id="compass">
      <img src="/images/compass.png" alt="compass" width="211" height="181" />
    </div>
    <div id="location">
      <p>One Memorial Drive, Cambridge, MA</p>
      <p class="venue">Microsoft NERD Center</p>
      <p class="date">11am - 4pm, february 5th, 2011</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <hr class="top"/>
  <div class="register-button top clearfix">
    <div class="hand left"></div>
    <h2><a href="#registration">register now</a></h2>
    <div class="hand right"></div>
  </div>
</section>
<div id="main-bottom"></div>
<section id="schedule">
  <header>
    <h1>Schedule</h1>
  </header>
  <p id="schedule-info">Students will eat, hear some talks, then meet designers and developers from startups. The talks are short and motivational. Many focus on one technology or technique which is currently in high demand by startups. Students will hear why it's awesome and some of the cool things you can do with it. They will not be introductory tutorials. We're <%= link_to "carefully curating resources", page_path("what") %> for further study on each topic.</p>
