      <p class="event-speaker double">Caroline Hadilaksono &amp; <br />Micah Rich (A Good Company)</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="event-time">11:50am</p>
      <p class="event-title"><%= link_to "A Day in the Life of a Developer", page_path("what", :anchor => "a-day-in-the-life-of-a-developer") %></p>
      <p class="event-speaker">Dharmesh Shah (HubSpot)</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="event-time">12:00pm</p>
      <p class="event-title"><%= link_to "User Experience", page_path("what", :anchor => "user-experience") %></p>
      <p class="event-speaker">Ben Pieratt (Svpply)</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="event-time">12:10pm</p>
      <p class="event-title"><%= link_to "Typography", page_path("what", :anchor => "typography") %></p>
      <p class="event-speaker">Annie Wang (Her Campus)</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="event-time">12:20pm</p>
      <p class="event-title"><%= link_to "Grids", page_path("what", :anchor => "grids") %></p>
      <p class="event-speaker">Chad Mazzola (thoughtbot)</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="event-time">12:30pm</p>
      <p class="event-title"><%= link_to "Text Editor", page_path("what", :anchor => "text-editor") %></p>
